content: Yes, "Jolene" is a classic Dolly Parton song that has become one of the most popular country music songs of all time. The song tells the story of a woman begging Jolene, another woman, not to steal her man, and has become famous for its haunting melody, emotional lyrics, and powerful vocals by Dolly Parton. In addition to "Jolene," Dolly Parton has written and performed many other memorable country music songs, including "Coat of Many Colors," "9 to 5," and "I Will Always Love You." Dolly Parton is also known for her philanthropic work and her involvement in various social causes.
